<h1>加拿大野火持续 消防员招聘难</h1>
<p>Author: 联合早报 (Person)</p>
<p>Publisher: 联合早报 (Organization)</p>
<p>Published Time: 2023-06-25T08:43</p>
<p>Modified Time: 2023-06-25T09:17</p>
